race.comment: HYPERGAMY (6) is a two-start maiden who looks close to a win after placing at both runs, the latest when third over 1609m in Listed grade at Del Mar (Turf). Should be prominent from the outset. Will give a great sight. YURAK (10) did a fair job on debut last time out, finishing a nose from the winner in second over 1609m at Del Mar (Turf). Should improve sharply and this looks a nice race. TIZ GRACE (7) is a two-start maiden who looks close to a win after placing at both runs, the latest when third over 1609m at Del Mar (Turf). Should be prominent from the outset. One of the main contenders. CONQUISTADORA (8) is on debut. By Justify and hails from the M W McCarthy stable. Worth watching for a betting push.
